  <div class="sk-cube sk-cube9">
    &nbsp; 
  </div> 
 </div> 
</div> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<h3 id="toc2" class="bonfire"><a name="x--Notes"></a>Notes</h3> 
<ul> 
 <li>Dragon Torso ability adds Damage buff, which lasts for around 6 seconds</li> 
 <li>Damage buff stacks with oath of sunlight</li> 
 <li>Consumes 102 stamina on use&nbsp;</li> 
</ul> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
